                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-260-off1461 t18320906-260-cd1462"></join>, 2 rings, value 6s.; 4 boxes, value 12s.; 2 spoons, value 5s.; 1 case, value 1s.; 14 yards of silk, value 30s.; 11 yards of persian, value 16s.; 1 pair of ear-rings and drops, value 7s.; 1 pair of stockings, value 1s.; 2 necklaces, value 7s.; 11 yards of gingham, value 2s.; 3 towels, value 1s.; 2 dresses, value 5s.; 1 comb, value 5s.; 1 shawl, value 6d.; 1 Bible, value 17s.; 1 brooch, value 3s.; 1 breast-pin, value 2s.; half a yard of calico-velvet, value 3s.; 1 fan, value 4d.; 1 locket, value 3s.; 5 yards of calico, value 2s.; 1 piece of foreign gold coin, value 36s.; 1 half-guinea, 1 half-crown, one shilling, and 1 sixpence, the property of 
                     
