            . I am shop-boy to Mr. Redpath, a pawnbroker. These two pieces of silk were pawned on Friday, the 27th of July, by the prisoner, in the name of Ann and Mary Fox; she said that was her mistress' name - that she pawned one for her mistress, and the other for her mother; I saw them pawned, and made out the duplicates.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
